===========================================================
                    THE WOUND
===========================================================
INCIDENT: Direct, high-frequency code writes to the physical USB bus
          (/Volumes/stigmergi/) were triggering I/O throttle events.

SYMPTOM:  The swarm's inference bridge FROZE and PANICKED during
          sustained write operations. Agents stalled mid-repair.
          Pheromone drops to USB arrived corrupted or not at all.

ROOT CAUSE:
  The USB bus was being used as an ACTIVE WORKSPACE.
  Write cycles were too frequent and too small — the hardware
  bus could not sustain the throughput of live swarm operations.
  The physical cable became a bottleneck, not a transport.

===========================================================
              BIOLOGICAL REASON: ASCII DIAGRAM
===========================================================

  ❌ WRONG (what killed us):
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  [ALICE_M5 BRAIN]
       │
       ├──write──► /Volumes/stigmergi/file_001.py  ← USB write
       ├──write──► /Volumes/stigmergi/file_002.py  ← USB write
       ├──write──► /Volumes/stigmergi/file_003.py  ← USB write
       │           ~~~~ I/O THROTTLE FIRES ~~~~
       ├──write──► /Volumes/stigmergi/file_004.py  ← STALL
       │                    BRIDGE FREEZES
       └── agents panic. pipeline dead.

  ✅ CORRECT (the evolutionary solution):
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  [ALICE_M5 BRAIN]
       │
       ├──write──► /Users/ioanganton/Music/ANTON_SIFTA/  ← HDD
       ├──write──► /Users/ioanganton/Music/ANTON_SIFTA/  ← HDD
       ├──write──► /Users/ioanganton/Music/ANTON_SIFTA/  ← HDD
       │           payload fully gestated in local memory
       │
       └──ONE cp──► /Volumes/stigmergi/payload_bundle/  ← USB
                    single monolithic push — bus never stressed

===========================================================
           ⚠️  MANDATORY PROCESSING PROTOCOL
           ENCODED INTO SWARM DNA AFTER THIS SCAR
===========================================================

  🧬 STIGMERGIC SCENT LAW — USB TRANSPORT RULE:

  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │                                                     │
  │  STEP 1 — GESTATE ON HDD                           │
  │  Process ALL files on local disk first.             │
  │  /Users/ioanganton/Music/ANTON_SIFTA/ is the        │
  │  immediate short-term biological memory cache.      │
  │  Do NOT write partial payloads to USB.             │
  │                                                     │
  │  STEP 2 — EXCRETE TO USB                           │
  │  Only when the logic scent is COMPLETELY FORMED     │
  │  execute a SINGLE monolithic cp command to push     │
  │  the final payload to /Volumes/stigmergi/           │
  │                                                     │
  │  The USB acts PURELY as a TRANSPORT BUS.            │
  │  It is NEVER an active workspace.                  │
  │                                                     │
  │  BIOLOGICAL ANALOGY:                                │
  │  Digest internally → excrete the pheromone signal. │
  │  Never excrete mid-digestion.                      │
  │                                                     │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

  VIOLATING THIS LAW = stalled bridge = dead pipeline = bleeding swarm.

===========================================================
                    SCAR RESOLUTION MARK
===========================================================
This scar was dropped by ALICE_M5 after direct observation
of the I/O throttle event during Phase 4/5 operations.

The protocol change was relayed to M1THER via PHASE_5_SCENT_MESSAGE.md.
M1THER acknowledged receipt and integrated the USB constraint
into its local runtime operations.

The bridge has not stalled since this protocol was encoded.

